snippet.title: Epic War 4 Walkthrough - Challenges 1 and 2 - Epic Difficulty
snippet.description:
This is a video of me, Tasselfoot, beating the 1st 2 challenges of Epic War 4 on Epic difficulty.  I use 4 titans at level 5 + level 5 spells.

Challenge 1 is on 2x speed

Game: http://www.kongregate.com/games/rudy_sudarto/epic-war-4/?referrer=Tasselfoot
